<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-restarNumDeDosDigitos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>40: I knew that 5 tens minus 1 ten is 4 tens and 4 tens is 40.</li>
      <li>48: I knew that <m>50 - 10</m> is 40, so this is just 8 more. </li>
      <li>238: I counted back by tens 258, 248, 238.</li>
      <li>234: This is just like the last one, but I took away 4 more.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


